{
    "global": {
        "clean_previous_files": true,
        "backup_previous_files": false,
        "backup_directory": "_extractor_backups",
        "include_timestamp_in_filename": false,
        "max_chars_per_file": 100000000,
        "show_compression_stats": true
    },
    "profiles": {
        "scripts": {
            "enabled": true,
            "description": "C# scripts with token-efficient compression",
            "directories": [
                "Assets/Scripts",
                "Assets/Editor"
            ],
            "blacklist_directories": [],
            "include_extensions": [".cs"],
            "exclude_extensions": [".meta"],
            "output_filename": "Unity_EXTRACTED_scripts",
            "part_output_filename": "Unity_EXTRACTED_scripts_part",
            "compression": {
                "enabled": true,
                "remove_empty_lines": true,
                "remove_comments": true,
                "remove_xml_docs": true,
                "remove_using_statements": true,
                "remove_regions": true,
                "remove_attributes": true,
                "trim_whitespace": true,
                "compress_braces": true,
                "compress_method_signatures": true,
                "compress_namespaces": true,
                "shorten_modifiers": true,
                "reduce_indentation": true,
                "indent_size": 1,
                "extreme_compression": false,
                "common_usings": [
                    "using System;",
                    "using System.Collections;",
                    "using System.Collections.Generic;",
                    "using UnityEngine;",
                    "using UnityEngine.UI;",
                    "using System.Linq;",
                    "using UnityEngine.Events;"
                ]
            },
            "include_toc": true,
            "compact_toc": true,
            "header_text": "UNITY PROJECT SCRIPTS - COMPRESSED FORMAT\nCompression Stats: {original_size:,} -> {compressed_size:,} chars ({saved_percent:.1f}% reduction)\nEstimated tokens saved: ~{tokens_saved:,}\n\nThis document contains extracted Unity 6 C# scripts optimized for AI/LLM context.\n\nWhen editing: return each changed method in full. If edits touch <=3 methods, list those blocks only; otherwise output the entire script. Always copy-paste ready.\n\nCOMPRESSION APPLIED:\n- Removed: empty lines, common usings, XML docs, most attributes, regions\n- Preserved: code structure, logic flow, important comments (TODO/FIXME/NOTE)\n\nWHEN CREATING/EDITING SCRIPTS:\n1. Re-add standard Unity using statements (listed below + any project-specific ones)\n2. Format with proper indentation and spacing\n3. Add [SerializeField] attributes where needed\n4. Ensure proper C# code style\n\nCOMMON USING STATEMENTS:\nusing System;\nusing System.Collections;\nusing System.Collections.Generic;\nusing UnityEngine;\nusing UnityEngine.UI;\nusing System.Linq;\nusing UnityEngine.Events;\n\nTABLE OF CONTENTS:"
        },
